node.text:
An Aegean Adventure • A collection of memories spanning 4 Grecian islands: Crete, Santorini, Corfu & Rhodes. 
This was a special campaign to be apart of, not only to be joined by friends who feature within this video, but also as a Tourism Board X @AegeanAirlines collaboration was my first job since the pandemic started. Greece has done a phenomenal job at vaccinating entire island populations to open up their country to the world, where so many can’t wait to visit & return. ✈️🇬🇷 We’ll all be back soon to explore what the mainland has to offer.

Link in bio to check out @AegeanAirlines’ discount offers on direct flights to destinations across Greece this summer! #AegeanAirlines #SunshineDiscount #VisitGreece

Team featured: @postcardsbyhannah @delphinepolson @lebackpacker @offthepath @wonguy974 @brubol @mpapa_dop @travlrr_official

node.text: Macao in 60 seconds..🇲🇴 a city like no other - a place where East meets West in a fusion of culture, architecture and cuisine. From the city’s lights, enchanting sights & market delights - here’s a little montage of our 4 days of discovery. • @MacaoUSA @Expedia #VisitMacao #WowMacao #Sp 📽 : Captured & edited by @dominic_doring - wouldn’t have been an epic trip with out ya mate!

A few moments from my time in Abu Dhabi...🐪✨🇦🇪 Earlier this month, myself & @dominic_doring ventured to this incredible Emirate in search of adventure, culture & camels. Safe to say, this experience will stay with me for a lifetime. Huge thanks to @VisitAbuDhabi for making this trip one for the books! #InAbuDhabi.
Videography by the amazingly talented, @dominic_doring. Be sure to check out his socials for more of his creations. 🤘🏽📽

ad Journey to completion…✨🇪🇸 Barcelona was our last point of call onboard @CelebrityCruisesUK's newest ship Celebrity Apex ship. I decided to stay on an extra day after we docked to get a feel for the city & it's safe to say, it's one I'd love to live in for a few months. My time at sea was one I won't forget. From sipping cocktails on the Rooftop Garden at sunset to watching the insanely talented theatre performances or dancing till 2am - cheers for all the good times. 🛳🥂🌊 

#celebrityapex #celebritycruisesuk

#barcelona #bcn #mediterranean

node.text:
A summer throwback…✨🇬🇷 
Three shots & a video from a September adventure to two of Greece’s most thriving cities - Athens & Thessaloniki - as well as the majestic Meteora.  An ancient capital, a foodie haven & a bucket list location made for a unforgettable trip.  Cheers for the good times @aegeanairlines x @visitgreecegr! 🤘🏼

For those planning to visit Greece next year, @AegeanAirlines are offering up to 40% off on direct flights to Corfu, Crete, Santorini & Rhodes from destinations across Europe! Offer on until end of December’21. Search up Sunshine Discount for more details. 

#AegeanAirlines #SunshineDiscount #VisitGreece #Athens #Thessalonki #Meteora

node.text:
ad First light over the Parthenon...🏛✨ Athens has pretty much played my home away from home this year. It so happened to be the starting point for @CelebrityCruisesUK's week-long voyage onboard their newest ship, the Celebrity Apex, which I had the pleasure of jumping aboard. 🛳🌊 Over 7 days, we covered 3 countries across the Mediterranean, stopping at Santorini to Messina, Mallorca ending in Barcelona. For someone who's a complete cruise trip rookie like me, the onboard experience was wild. It was practically a thriving city on water with top notch entertainment & food around the clock! Here are a few snaps from the trip.

#celebrityapex #celebritycruisesuk

#athens #greece #mediterranean

node.text:
My favourite photos from Greece so far…✨📸 

Excited to add to this capture catalogue from my current time in Athens & Thessaloniki soon. I’m then going onto Meteora, a destination a 3h drive from Thessaloniki which has been on my bucket list to visit for years.⛰📸 Ancient monasteries built onto mountain tops - have you heard of it?

node.text:
Sunset stages… 🌅✨
Day or night? Blue hour in Oia is it’s most magical time for me. The white washed caldera turns indigo and warm lights turn on, creating a cosy scene straight out of a storybook.

node.text:
📍Balos, Crete | Europe’s tropical lagoon 🏖 

Considered one of the best beaches in Europe, Balos’ white sand, crystal waters & exotic feel makes it easy to see why. Chania is the nearest city, full of Venetian charm & character & makes a perfect base for trip to Crete. 🤓🗺

📍Old Town, Corfu | Daybreak at Kings Landing ✨

Easily one of Greece’s most picturesque towns. In a sea of red & orange, Venetian townhouses meet impressive palaces. Life kinda slows down here & I just love that. 🤌🏼
